When the user selects <i>image</i> in the <i>type</i> field a text field shown below the <i>type</i> field with a <i>browse</i> button next to it. Here the user can manually type the location of the image he wants to add or select browse and his file directory will be displayed and he can navigate to and select the desired image. This is shown in figure 2.2.10. </p>
