<p><p><p>
The <i>replace</i> and <i>delete</i> buttons coorespond to attributes as well as questions. If an attribute is selected and the <i>replace</i> button is clicked then the add an attribute dialog will open. The index will automatically be filled in with the same index as the attribute being replaced. The user will still have the ability to change it however. If an attribute is selected and the <i>delete</i> button is clicked, the selected attribute will be removed from the test. 
